## 🌟 What Is This?

The **Faculty Academic Activity Tracker** is a **single HTML file** web application that allows faculty to:

| 🎯 Feature | 💬 Description |
|---|---|
| 📝 **Enter activities online** | Fill forms directly in the browser — no Excel, no software needed |
| ☁️ **Firebase sync** | Data saved to Firebase Realtime Database — visible on all devices instantly |
| 📊 **Live dashboard** | Charts and stats update the moment you save an entry |
| 📅 **Any academic year** | Type `2016-17`, `2020-21`, `2025-26` — no dropdown restriction |
| 📋 **NAAC-ready summary** | Auto-count by year across all 43 activity categories |
| ⬇️ **CSV export** | Download all records for reports and AQAR submission |
| 📱 **Responsive** | Works on desktop, laptop, tablet, and mobile |
| 🔓 **No login required** | Anyone with the link can enter data |

