## 🗓️ Academic Year — Completely Free

> No dropdown. No restriction. Type **any year** you want.

```
Examples:  2014-15  |  2016-17  |  2018-19  |  2025-26  |  2030-31
```

The **Dashboard** and **Summary Table** automatically group and display all years found in your data.

